277
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:14,210
放学后才醒
When I woke up after school,

278
00:17:14,610 --> 00:17:17,280
我听到Reynolds校长在隔壁房间
In the other room, Principal Reynolds was there.

279
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:21,850
