if you didn't already know that I was.

357
00:21:51,870 --> 00:21:53,840
假设 你能
Could you, hypothetically,

358
00:21:54,090 --> 00:21:56,700
偷偷地打开别人的邮箱吗?
access someone's E-mail account without their knowledge?

359
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:58,860
我... 可以 看是什么样的邮箱
I... yeah, it depends on the account.

360
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:00,560
员工邮箱
Say a faculty account.

361
00:22:01,470 --> 00:22:02,400
假设是
Hypothetically.

362
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:07,040
- 谁的?  - Kondracki护士的
- Whose?  - Nurse Kondracki.

363
00:22:07,260 --> 00:22:09,210
Kim吗? 为什么? 你觉得她很辣?
Kim? Why? Do you got the hots for her?

364
00:22:09,220 --> 00:22:10,720
不 我只是...
No. I'm just...

365
00:22:11,580 --> 00:22:14,490
我只是对她的信件好奇
I'm curious about some of her correspondence.

366
00:22:16,555 --> 00:22:17,705
跟谁的信?
With whom?

367
00:22:21,465 --> 00:22:23,385
好吧 算了
Okay. That's fine.

368
00:22:23,595 --> 00:22:25,805
我没找你 是你找上的我
I didn't come to see you. You came to see me.

369
00:22:25,805 --> 00:22:28,015
我没时间回答你的问题
I don't have time to play 20 questions.

370
00:22:28,245 --> 00:22:29,935
你要不就告诉我 你在做什么
Now you can either tell me what it is that you're doing,

371
00:22:29,935 --> 00:22:34,115
- 要不就让我安安静静地改作业  - 好吧 好吧
- or you can let me finish grading my papers in peace.  - All right, all right.

372
00:22:34,995 --> 00:22:37,795
我有理由相信 她也许
I have reason to believe that she might be engaged

373
00:22:37,805 --> 00:22:41,205
跟Reynolds校长有
in an inappropriate personal relationship

374
00:22:41,205 --> 00:22:42,625
不正当的关系
with Principal Reynolds.

375
00:22:44,665 --> 00:22:45,885
你有预谋的
You're making a play.

376
00:22:46,835 --> 00:22:49,105
你在预谋件大事 对吗?
You're going after the big job, aren't you?

377
00:22:49,105 --> 00:22:51,525
Leslie 你要不要帮我?
Are you going to help me or not, Leslie?

378
00:22:54,635 --> 00:22:56,285
我想要个好位子
I want a good spot.

379
00:22:56,555 --> 00:22:57,465
你说什么?
I'm sorry?

380
00:22:57,695 --> 00:23:00,475
我想要Lamr在主停车场的停车位...
I want Lamr's spot in the main parking lot...

381
00:23:00,475 --> 00:23:01,525
在枫树旁边的那个
the one next to the maple tree.

382
00:23:01,525 --> 00:23:03,305
不是在枫树下边的... 是在旁边的那个
Not under the maple tree... next to the maple tree.

383
00:23:03,305 --> 00:23:04,695
这样的话 我的车会在树荫底下
That way, I get the shade from the maple tree

384
00:23:04,695 --> 00:23:06,965
但那些树渣子又不会掉到我车上
but not all that tree crap all over the hood of my car.

385
00:23:08,500 --> 00:23:11,070
我还想要实验服 很多实验服
And I want aprons. I want lots of aprons.

386
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:12,510
我还想要一些
And I want some lab equipment in here

387
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:16,500
- 近十年的实验器材 成交吗?  - 成交
- that was built in this decade. Is that a deal?  - Deal.

388
00:23:17,690 --> 00:23:21,440
你知道 你真的能让我解决那个混蛋
You know, you really had me fooled with that sweater vest.

389
00:23:23,140 --> 00:23:24,760
Linus 你才是真正的杀手
Linus, you're a real killer.

390
00:24:21,024 --> 00:24:22,314
之前来过这儿?
Been here before?

391
00:24:22,704 --> 00:24:23,794
是的
Yes.

392
00:24:26,984 --> 00:24:29,674
我在岛上这么久
And in all the time that I've spent on this island,

393
00:24:29,674 --> 00:24:32,194
今天是第一次回来这里
today is the first time I've ever come back.

394
00:24:32,544 --> 00:24:35,574
Jack? 哥们儿 你在哪儿?
Jack? Dude, where are ya?

395
00:24:35,584 --> 00:24:36,704
我在这儿
I'm in here.

396
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,780
别打开 那是甘油炸药
Do not open that. There's dynamite in there.

397
00:24:59,780 --> 00:25:01,230
- 那个极不稳定  - 我知道
- It's mega-unstable.  - I know.

398
00:25:01,230 --> 00:25:02,330
Arzt博士就是这样...
So did Dr. Arzt...

399
00:25:02,330 --> 00:25:04,740
两天后 我才把粉身碎骨的他 从我的衣服里清干净
Then I was wiping him out of my shirt two days later.

400
00:25:05,060 --> 00:25:07,110
- 哥们儿 该走了  - 不 还没到时候
- Dude, it's time to go.  - No, not yet.

401
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,350
他想打开那根甘油炸药
He's opening up a crate of dynamite,

402
00:25:09,350 --> 00:25:12,330
- 他还说过要自杀  - 我自杀不了
- and he said he wanted to kill himself.  - I can't kill myself.

403
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:13,960
什么?
What?

404
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:16,080
即便我想死... 相信我 我是认真的...
Even if I wanted to... and trust me, I do...

405
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:17,770
我... 我没有办法自杀
I... I can't kill myself.

406
00:25:18,650 --> 00:25:20,680
这也就是为什么 我要让你们替我下手
Which is why I want you to do it for me.

407
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:23,210
你到底在说些什么?
What are you talking about?

408
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:28,080
我所说的是 Jack 就是...
What I'm talking about, Jack, is that...

409
00:25:28,530 --> 00:25:29,740
好吧 Jacob碰过我
Well, Jacob touched me.

410
00:25:30,540 --> 00:25:34,040
当Jacob碰了你... 呃 这就算是大礼了吧
And when Jacob touches you... well, it's considered a gift.

411
00:25:34,470 --> 00:25:36,670
除非它根本不是
Except it's not a gift at all.

412
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:39,390
这是一个诅咒
It's a curse.

413
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:41,000
伙计!
Dude!

414
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,540
我说认真的 咱们现在该走了!
Seriously, let's go now!

415
00:25:42,830 --> 00:25:43,870
为什么你想死?
Why do you want to die?

416
00:25:44,810 --> 00:25:46,300
我将我...
I devoted my life...

417
00:25:47,250 --> 00:25:49,250
长到你无法想象的生命...
longer than you can possibly imagine...

418
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:51,960
奉献给 那个告诉我
in service of a man who told me

419
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:54,790
无风不起浪的人
that everything was happening for a reason,

420
00:25:54,791 --> 00:25:56,481
他说他有一个计划...
that he had a plan...

421
00:25:56,861 --> 00:25:58,761
我也是计划当中的一部分...
A plan that I was a part of...

422
00:25:59,141 --> 00:26:02,001
当时机成熟的时候 他就会告诉我前因后果
And when the time was right that he'd share it with me.

423
00:26:02,841 --> 00:26:04,041
但是现在 那个人死了
And now that man's gone.

424
00:26:04,041 --> 00:26:06,551
所以我为何想死?
So why do I want to die?

425
00:26:06,561 --> 00:26:09,621
因为我发现 我已经失去生活的目标了
Because I just found out my entire life had no purpose.

426
00:26:11,741 --> 00:26:14,761
哪怕我能亲手点燃这个炸药 它... 也不会炸的
Now if I light this myself, it... it won't work.

427
00:26:14,761 --> 00:26:16,641
但是你能帮我点燃 Jack
But you can light it for me, Jack.

428
00:26:17,331 --> 00:26:19,741
我会把导火线做得足够长 这样你就有时间跑出去
I made the fuse long enough so you'll have time to get out.

429
00:26:21,111 --> 00:26:23,651
Jack 求你告诉我 你不想这么做
Jack, please tell me you're not actually considering this.

430
00:26:25,051 --> 00:26:25,741
如果他执意去死
If he wants to die,

431
00:26:25,741 --> 00:26:27,311
我们无论如何也阻止不了
there's nothing we're gonna do to stop him.

432
00:26:34,561 --> 00:26:35,351
谢谢你
Thank you.

433
00:27:02,021 --> 00:27:02,741
现在...
Now...

434
00:27:05,321 --> 00:27:06,241
我们谈谈吧
Let's talk.

435
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:18,190
Jack! 伙计 我们得走了 他疯了 我知道他疯了
Jack! Dude, we gotta go. Guy's crazy, and I know crazy.

436
00:27:18,190 --> 00:27:20,530
- Hurley 你走吧 我们不会有事的  - 兄弟 你马上会被炸死的!
- Hurley, go ahead. We'll be all right.  - Dude, you're gonna blow up!

437
00:27:20,530 --> 00:27:24,650
- 我得和他谈谈 Hurley 你走吧  - 不 我不会丢下你不管的
- Gotta talk to him, Hurley. Just go.  - No, I'm not going without you.

438
00:27:24,650 --> 00:27:25,890
Hurley 我不会有事的
Hurley, I'll be fine.

439
00:27:31,482 --> 00:27:33,742
如果你改变主意的话 我会在 大概 一里外的地方等你
If you change your mind, I'll be, like, a mile away.

440
00:27:35,012 --> 00:27:37,972
- 你应该和他走的 Jack  - 不 Richard 不 我不会走的
- You should go with him, Jack.  - No, Richard. No, I shouldn't.

441
00:27:37,972 --> 00:27:39,062
不然你会死的
Then you're gonna die.

442
00:27:41,152 --> 00:27:43,532
事实上 我觉得我俩都死不了
Actually, I don't think either one of us is gonna die.

443
00:27:44,462 --> 00:27:45,642
你为何这么想?
What makes you think that?

444
00:27:45,982 --> 00:27:47,362
我刚从灯塔来
I just came from a lighthouse

445
00:27:48,842 --> 00:27:50,312
转盘上刻着我的名字
where my name was etched in wood

446
00:27:50,312 --> 00:27:52,292
使得镜子
on a dial that turned a mirror

447
00:27:53,742 --> 00:27:56,602
可以照出我从小到大住的 那栋房子的景象
that somehow reflected the image of the house that I grew up in.

448
00:28:00,262 --> 00:28:01,322
Jacob的灯塔
Jacob's lighthouse.

449
00:28:02,752 --> 00:28:03,942
他叫Hurley把我从这弄出去
He got Hurley to bring me out there

450
00:28:03,942 --> 00:28:06,482
因为他想让我看见镜子里所反射的景象
because he wanted me to see what was reflected in that mirror.

451
00:28:06,722 --> 00:28:08,432
基于某个原因 他想让我知道
For some reason, he wanted me to know

452
00:28:08,752 --> 00:28:11,322
当我还是个孩子的时候 他就开始注视我了
that he had been watching me ever since I was a kid.

453
00:28:13,802 --> 00:28:14,522
为什么?
Why?

454
00:28:15,672 --> 00:28:16,882
我不知道为什么
I have no idea why.

455
00:28:18,992 --> 00:28:21,422
但是我敢向你打赌 如果Jacob费了这么大力气
But I'm willing to bet you that if Jacob went to that trouble,

456
00:28:22,692 --> 00:28:24,932
基于某个原因把我弄到岛上来
that he brought me to this island for a reason,

457
00:28:25,212 --> 00:28:27,792
肯定不会让我跟你现在一起被炸死
and it's not to blow up sitting here with you right now.

458
00:28:29,312 --> 00:28:32,392
- 你在拿自己的命开玩笑啊 Jack  - 是的
- That's a pretty big risk you're taking, Jack.  - Yes.

459
00:28:33,192 --> 00:28:36,442
- 但如果你错了怎么办?  - 我不会错的
- What if you're wrong?  - I'm not.

460
00:29:06,900 --> 00:29:08,440
想再试一根吗?
Want to try another stick?

461
00:29:12,010 --> 00:29:13,280
好吧 Jack
All right, Jack.

462
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:17,030
你好像看破一切玄机了 那么... 现在该怎么办?
You seem to have all the answers. So... so now what?

463
00:29:18,110 --> 00:29:19,610
我们重回起点吧
We go back to where we started.

464
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,460
你好 Ben
Hello, Ben.

465
00:29:57,220 --> 00:29:58,520
你在这儿做什么呢?
What are you doing here?

466
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:01,270
参观啊 你又在干什么呢?
Visiting. What are you doing?

467
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:03,220
我在自掘坟墓
I'm digging my own grave.

468
00:30:04,440 --> 00:30:05,260
为什么?
Why?

469
00:30:07,330 --> 00:30:09,630
因为你骗我杀了Jacob
Because you talked me into killing Jacob.

470
00:30:11,590 --> 00:30:13,320
你看见那边吃芒果的那个女人了吗?
Do you see that woman over there eating a mango?

471
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:16,100
她是他的保镖 她知道我做了什么
She's his bodyguard, and she knows what I did.

472
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:20,360
你得偿所愿了 因为她要杀我
So you've got what you wanted because she's going to kill me.

473
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,430
我可不想要你死 Ben
I don't want you to die, Ben.

474
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:25,270
其实 我是回雕塑这儿来找你的
In fact, I went back to the statue to get you,

475
00:30:25,270 --> 00:30:28,840
- 但是你已经走了  - 找我? 为了什么?
- but you'd already gone.  - Get me? For what?

476
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:32,020
我正在召集一组人离开这里
I'm gathering a group to leave this place for good.

477
00:30:33,110 --> 00:30:34,780
但是一旦我们走了
But once we're gone,

478
00:30:35,040 --> 00:30:37,960
岛还需要人来接管
someone's gonna need to be in charge of the island.

479
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:41,220
我?
Me?

480
00:30:41,390 --> 00:30:43,990
我实在找不出比你更合适的人选
I can't think of a better man for the job.

481
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:46,530
哦 在这种情况下 可能性看上去不大吧
Well, it doesn't seem very likely, does it,

482
00:30:46,530 --> 00:30:48,340
对不?
under the circumstances?

483
00:30:48,340 --> 00:30:50,340
我怎么样才能离开...
How am I gonna get away from...

484
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:57,790
去另一个岛 去九头蛇站
Come to the other island, to the Hydra Station.

485
00:30:57,790 --> 00:31:01,380
- 那就是我们要去的地方  - 她会跟着我的
- That's where we'll be.  - She'll come after me.

486
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:03,680
往里走200码的地方 林中空地有一棵树
200 yards inland, there's a tree in the clearing

487
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:05,240
树上架了把来福枪
with a rifle leaning up against it.

488
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:07,230
如果现在走的话 你能第一个到那儿
If you go now, you'll get there first

489
00:31:07,230 --> 00:31:09,280
然后你就可以干掉她
and you'll have the drop on her.

490
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:12,350
但是千万别犹豫
But don't hesitate.

491
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:13,820
她可不会
She won't.

492
00:31:15,020 --> 00:31:16,530
待会见 Ben
See you soon, Ben.

493
00:31:33,170 --> 00:31:33,900
嘿!
Hey!

494
00:31:42,070 --> 00:31:44,100

Reynolds校长室

495
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:47,240
进来
Come in.

496
00:31:50,850 --> 00:31:52,030
Linus 我现在没有时间
Linus, I don't have time

497
00:31:52,030 --> 00:31:54,130
听你抱怨那些留堂生的事
to listen to you complain about detention.

498
00:31:54,130 --> 00:31:56,300
我不是为这个来的 我想让你看些东西
That's not why I'm here. I want you to read something.

499
00:31:57,730 --> 00:32:01,350
好吧 如果你想让你那个小社团...
Well, if this some attempt to revive your little club...

500
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:09,890
这些是3个月内的30封邮件
Those are 30 E-mails that cover a 3-month period.

501
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:15,220
这事还真淫乱
It's pretty lascivious stuff,

502
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:16,650
如果是私房事 也就罢了
which would be fine if it was private,

503
00:32:16,650 --> 00:32:17,850
但是它们好像描述的是
but they seem to describe

504
00:32:17,850 --> 00:32:20,840
发生在校园的行为...
acts that took place on school property...

505
00:32:21,530 --> 00:32:25,070
不知廉耻的行为
acts which, morality aside,

506
00:32:25,340 --> 00:32:27,470
我想学校董事会一定会不满
I think the school board would frown on,

507
00:32:27,470 --> 00:32:29,060
更别说你的妻子
not to mention your wife.

508
00:32:33,130 --> 00:32:34,740
你想要什么?
What do you want?

509
00:32:35,820 --> 00:32:38,820
你的职位
Your job.

510
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:40,640
你要辞职...
You're gonna resign...

511
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:42,300
原因是 比如...
for, I don't know...

512
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:45,010
一些个人理由 健康问题之类 随便你掰
personal reasons, health. Your call.

513
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:47,230
在你辞职的同时 你要向校董事会
But with your resignation, you're gonna recommend

514
00:32:47,230 --> 00:32:49,670
推荐我来接替你的职位
that the school board hire me as your replacement.

515
00:32:50,610 --> 00:32:51,850
讽刺的是
And the irony of all this

516
00:32:51,850 --> 00:32:54,010
他们会因为对你的尊敬
is that they hold you in such esteem

517
00:32:54,610 --> 00:32:56,500
而让我真的坐上这个位子
that I'll get the job.

518
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:00,610
那... 我们达成共识了吗?
So... do we have an understanding?

519
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:08,100
Linus啊...
Linus...

520
00:33:08,650 --> 00:33:10,900
我能给你读一封电子邮件吗?
May I read you an E-mail?

521
00:33:19,660 --> 00:33:20,680
"亲爱的Reynolds校长"
"Dear Principal Reynolds,

522
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:22,200
"如果您能为我向耶鲁大学写
"I would appreciate it if you could write

523
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:26,400
"一封推荐信 我将感激涕零
"a letter of recommendation to Yale on my behalf.

524
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:28,020
"这对我很重要
"It would mean the world to me.

525
00:33:28,020 --> 00:33:30,340
致礼 Alexandra Rousseau"
Sincerely, Alexandra Rousseau."

526
00:33:31,665 --> 00:33:34,705
推荐信这种事真有趣 Linus
It's a funny thing about recommendations, Linus.

527
00:33:35,435 --> 00:33:37,075
