They work both ways.

528
00:33:37,775 --> 00:33:39,075
所以...
So...

529
00:33:39,075 --> 00:33:41,915
我把这个难题抛给你
I put the ball back in your court.

530
00:33:43,435 --> 00:33:47,045
你可以施展你的小手段
You can execute your little machiavellian maneuvers,

531
00:33:47,045 --> 00:33:49,795
争取我的工作 坐我的办公桌
go for my job, sit at my desk.

532
00:33:49,795 --> 00:33:53,575
但是 唉 不幸的副作用...
But, alas, there will be an unfortunate side effect...

533
00:33:54,065 --> 00:33:56,825
我能给Rousseau小姐
I will torch Miss Rousseau

534
00:33:56,825 --> 00:33:58,515
灿烂的前程
and her future.

535
00:33:59,905 --> 00:34:04,545
我的职位和权力 对你这么重要吗?
Is my job, my power, that important to you?

536
00:34:07,735 --> 00:34:09,455
那么...
So...

537
00:34:09,685 --> 00:34:12,755
你的抉择是什么 Linus博士?
What'll it be, Dr. Linus?

538
00:34:31,615 --> 00:34:33,295
放下!
Drop it!

539
00:34:33,295 --> 00:34:34,805
把枪放下!
Put the gun down!

540
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:53,680
你还等什么?
What are you waiting for?

541
00:34:56,240 --> 00:34:58,070
我想要解释
I want to explain.

542
00:34:58,590 --> 00:35:00,200
解释什么?
Explain what?

543
00:35:00,290 --> 00:35:04,390
我想要解释 我知道你的感受
I want to explain that I know what you're feeling.

544
00:35:04,910 --> 00:35:07,110
你不知道我的感受
You have no idea what I'm feeling.

545
00:35:08,090 --> 00:35:11,820
我看着我的女儿Alex 死在我面前
I watched my daughter Alex die in front of me.

546
00:35:13,250 --> 00:35:15,250
而且是我造成的
And it was my fault.

547
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:21,230
我有机会救她的
I had a chance to save her,

548
00:35:22,410 --> 00:35:24,590
但是我选择了小岛...
but I chose the island...

549
00:35:24,990 --> 00:35:26,400
而不是她
over her.

550
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:30,240
都是为了Jacob
All in the name of Jacob.

551
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:35,100
我为他牺牲了一切...
I sacrificed everything for him...

552
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:40,560
他甚至都不在乎
and he didn't even care.

553
00:35:43,170 --> 00:35:44,200
是 我捅死了他
Yeah, I stabbed him.

554
00:35:44,200 --> 00:35:47,470
我... 很生气...
I was... so angry..

555
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:49,100
昏了头
confused.

556
00:35:49,100 --> 00:35:53,080
我... 我担心失去
I... I was terrified that I was about to lose

557
00:35:53,080 --> 00:35:55,540
对我唯一重要的东西...
the only thing that had ever mattered to me...

558
00:35:55,540 --> 00:35:57,240
权力
My power.

559
00:35:58,910 --> 00:36:02,190
但是真正重要的东西...
But the thing that really mattered...

560
00:36:03,930 --> 00:36:05,350
已经没了
was already gone.

561
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:10,130
很抱歉我杀了Jacob
I'm sorry that I killed Jacob.

562
00:36:11,140 --> 00:36:12,460
真的
I am.

563
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:15,330
但是我也不指望你原谅我
And I do not expect you to forgive me

564
00:36:15,330 --> 00:36:17,560
因为...
Because...

565
00:36:18,479 --> 00:36:21,199
我不能原谅自己
I can never forgive myself.

566
00:36:23,309 --> 00:36:24,769
那么你想要什么?
Then what do you want?

567
00:36:26,659 --> 00:36:29,289
只要... 放我走
Just... let me leave.

568
00:36:31,759 --> 00:36:33,409
你要去哪?
Where will you go?

569
00:36:35,849 --> 00:36:37,579
去找Locke
To Locke.

570
00:36:38,509 --> 00:36:39,969
为什么?
Why?

571
00:36:40,159 --> 00:36:43,679
因为只有他能收留我
Because he's the only one that'll have me.

572
00:36:49,439 --> 00:36:51,019
我会收留你
I'll have you.

573
00:37:26,009 --> 00:37:27,239

Donald Lawrence Reynolds校长

574
00:37:38,366 --> 00:37:39,496
Linus博士
Dr. Linus.

575
00:37:39,496 --> 00:37:43,396
- 您好啊 Alex  - 我顺路来感谢Reynolds校长
- Hello, Alex.  - I was just coming by to thank Principal Reynolds.

576
00:37:43,396 --> 00:37:46,276
他给我写了一封不可思议的推荐信
He wrote me the most incredible letter of recommendation.

577
00:37:46,276 --> 00:37:47,766
哇 太好了
Wow. Wonderful.

578
00:37:48,516 --> 00:37:50,576
是您起了作用吗?
Did you have something to do with it?

579
00:37:50,726 --> 00:37:52,916
我是说 我原本以为他可能会说些好话
I mean, I thought he might say some nice things,

580
00:37:52,916 --> 00:37:56,956
- 但是他好话都说绝了 - 不 跟我没关系 Alex
- but he really went all out.  - No, it wasn't me, Alex.

581
00:37:56,956 --> 00:37:58,496
但是大家都说 你是个优秀的学生
But it always say you're a great student.

582
00:37:58,496 --> 00:38:00,716
很明显 不只有我能看到
Obviously, I wasn't the only one who noticed.

583
00:38:01,467 --> 00:38:02,007
谢谢你 博士...
Thanks, doctor...

584
00:38:02,007 --> 00:38:04,487
Linus 你他妈的在我办公室里干啥呢?
Linus, what the hell are you doing in my office?

585
00:38:05,927 --> 00:38:08,737
应你的要求 来送这周留堂生的
Just dropping off the detention sign-up sheet for the week,

586
00:38:08,737 --> 00:38:10,467
登记表
per your request.

587
00:38:10,587 --> 00:38:12,647
放我桌上就行
Just put it on my desk.

588
00:38:15,437 --> 00:38:17,207
那么我们历史社团见?
So will I see you at history club?

589
00:38:17,457 --> 00:38:20,707
- 啊 您是说何时重新搞活动吗?  - 哦 不 我们按原计划进行
- Uh, you mean when it's back on?  - Oh, no, we've got our old slot back.

590
00:38:20,707 --> 00:38:22,907
Reynolds校长找了别人监管留堂生
Principal Reynolds found someone to cover for detention.

591
00:38:22,907 --> 00:38:24,207
是不是?
Isn't that right?

592
00:38:26,100 --> 00:38:27,510
是 没错
Yes, that's right.

593
00:38:27,870 --> 00:38:30,010
哦 好吧 下午4点见
Well, then, see you at 4:00.

594
00:38:30,010 --> 00:38:31,510
再见
Bye.

595
00:38:40,940 --> 00:38:43,280
嘿 事情办成了吗?
Hey. Did you do it?

596
00:38:44,470 --> 00:38:45,540
没有
No.

597
00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:46,780
没有?
No?

598
00:38:47,410 --> 00:38:48,870
没有?! 等等
No?! Wait.

599
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:51,510
我... 我的停车位呢?
What... what about my parking space?

600
00:38:51,510 --> 00:38:52,940
你可以用我的
You can have mine.

601
00:40:03,350 --> 00:40:05,300
需要帮忙吗?
Do you need a hand?

602
00:40:07,330 --> 00:40:09,270
帮我弄下苫布
Please help me with the tarp.

603
00:42:10,500 --> 00:42:13,250
长官 海滩上有人
Sir, there are people on the beach.

604
00:42:13,960 --> 00:42:15,120
我们要停下来吗?
Should we stop?

605
00:42:15,170 --> 00:42:16,780
不
No.

606
00:42:17,770 --> 00:42:19,110
照计划行事
Proceed as planned.

607
00:42:19,110 --> 00:42:21,180
遵命 Widmore先生

Yes, sir, Mr. Widmore.

